prodNameC: 羅氏可霸斯e醣類抗原19-9檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
M  Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL:Streptavidin-coated    microparticles 0.72 mg/mL;preservative.
R1  Anti-CA19-9-Ab~biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL:Biotinylated monoclonal anti-CA19-9 antibody (mouse) 3mg/L;phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L; pH6.5; preservative.
R2  Anti-CA19-9-Ab~Ru(bpy)2+3(black cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL:Monoclonal anti-CA19-9 antibody (mouse)labeled with ruthenium complex 4 mg/L; phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L; pH 6.5; preservative.

CalSet - working solutions
CA19-9 Cal1:2 bottles, each for 1.0mL of calibrator 1
CA19-9 Cal2:2 bottles, each for 1.0mL of calibrator 2
CA19-9 (human) in two concentration ranges (approx. 20 U/mL and approx. 250 U/mL) in a human serum matrix; preservative.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: 用於體外定量檢測人類血清及血漿中CA 19-9的免疫分析法。Electro chemiluminescence immunoassay“ECLIA”是預定使用於 Elecsys和cobas e免疫分析儀上。Elecsys CA 19-9 CalSet是使用在Elecsys和cobas e免疫分析儀上,以供校正定量的Elecsys CA 19-9分析法之校正液組。
